full_text:
Jhake Angelo Cunanan Vargas , better known as Jake Vargas, is a Filipino television actor who played the role of young Tristan in GMA Network's remake of the Koreanovela Stairway To Heaven.
Vargas appeared in the GMA hit shows such as Reel Love Presents: Tween Hearts, Captain Barbell and Home Sweet Home. He is currently a regular in Pepito Manaloto, Sunday All Stars and Walang Tulugan with the Master Showman, in where he is frequently called as the "Prince of Mall Shows." His manager is the King of late-night variety shows, German Moreno also known as Kuya Germs.
title: Jake Vargas
